fields.name: Enabled
fields.description: True if configuration is enabled, false if it is disabled and null if configuration is not set.

fields.name: RetentionInDays
fields.description:
Retention in days.
Remove blobs older than X days.
0 or lower means no retention.

fields.name: SasUrl
fields.description: SAS url to a azure blob container with read/write/list/delete permissions.
